      "date": "2011-11-10 13:30:40.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nAlex, could you just rebase your work over this patch? I think OSD API changes will be smaller a bit and easier to review.\n\nJames, I don't see big code overlapping with ORNL-3 changes so conflict would be easily fixed, meanwhile I can't set my patch dependent on ORNL-3 because I don't know the order they will landed by. Usually there is only one rule - you snooze, you lose. In any case someone will need to update own patch over the latest tree.\n\nOleg is the only person who can set such order, I'll ask him about ORNL-3 landing plans at first",
